race.comment: Complexion of the race has changed after key scratchings. SKIEDA (12) shapes as the main beneficiary of those. Was well found when resuming and where there's smoke there's fire. Will strop fitter for that run and should take beating in this line up. CHARMED CHOICE (5) is on debut but is sure to be well-educated from the champion Waller yard. Respect any market confidence. BLENHEIM GIRL (13) rounds out the selections. Ran fourth on debut at Doomben. Will have derived valuable race experience and fitness from that run. Bred to appreciate the rise to 1400m. PEAK MISS (10) showed good improvement second up at this course and distance. Will be doing her best work late.
